g-allaccademia-di-santa-cecilia/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Recital di Yuja Wang all’Accademia di Santa Cecilia</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/02/cremona-teatro-ponchielli-il-balletto-civile-con-in-erme/" rel="next">Cremona, Teatro Ponchielli: il Balletto Civile con &#8220;In-erme&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2015/02/venezia-teatro-la-fenice-don-pasquale/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sarà pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_post_ID' value='79493' id='comment_post_ID' /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_parent' id='comment_parent' value='0' /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="akismet_comment_nonce" name="akismet_comment_nonce" value="4748c3dd9e" /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="ak_js" name="ak_js" value="93"/></p></form></div></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedposts-widget-2" class="widget ct-relatedposts-widget clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">Articoli correlati</h3><ul class="related-posts-single clearfix"><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42-festival-della-valle-ditria-la-grotta-di-trofonio/' title='Martina Franca, 42° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="la grotta di Trofonio, Martina Franca 2016" title="Martina Franca, 42° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/opera-di-firenze-cortile-di-palazzo-pitti-la-traviata/' title='Opera di Firenze, Cortile di Palazzo Pitti: &#8220;La Traviata&#8221;'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="La traviata (prima) Simone Donati - TerraProject - Contrasto (10)" title="Opera di Firenze, Cortile di Palazzo Pitti: &#8220;La Traviata&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/i-puritani-al-teatro-real-di-madrid/' title='“I Puritani” al Teatro Real di Madrid'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Madrid, Teatro Real, 11 VII 2016 (I Puritani) 8" title="“I Puritani” al Teatro Real di Madrid" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-11-VII-2016-I-Puritani-8-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/roma-terme-di-caracalla-stagione-lirica-2016-nabucco/' title='Roma, Terme di Caracalla, Stagione Lirica 2016: &#8220;Nabucco&#8221;'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Nabucco_Il-coro-nel-Va-pensiero_Yasuko-Kageyama-Opera-di-Roma-Caracalla-2016_7566-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Nabucco_Il coro nel Va pensiero_Yasuko Kageyama-Opera di Roma, Caracalla 2016_7566" title="Roma, Terme di Caracalla, Stagione Lirica 2016: &#8220;Nabucco&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Nabucco_Il-coro-nel-Va-pensiero_Yasuko-Kageyama-Opera-di-Roma-Caracalla-2016_7566-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Nabucco_Il-coro-nel-Va-pensiero_Yasuko-Kageyama-Opera-di-Roma-Caracalla-2016_7566-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/staatsoper-stuttgart-i-puritani/' title='Staatsoper Stuttgart: &#8220;I Puritani&#8221;'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/41852_puritani__hpo_33-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="puritani, stuttgart, 2016" title="Staatsoper Stuttgart: &#8220;I Puritani&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/41852_puritani__hpo_33-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/41852_puritani__hpo_33-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/milano-teatro-alla-scala-simon-boccanegra-cast-alternativo/' title='Milano, Teatro alla Scala: &#8220;Simon Boccanegra&#8221; (cast alternativo)'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/scala-boccanegra-3-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="scala-boccanegra-3" title="Milano, Teatro alla Scala: &#8220;Simon Boccanegra&#8221; (cast alternativo)" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/scala-boccanegra-3-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/scala-boccanegra-3-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li></ul> </aside></div></div></div><div id="footer" role="contentinfo"><div class="container"><div class="row-fluid"><div class="span6"><div class="copyright-info"> Associazione Culturale GB Opera<br/>Sede legale: vicolo Scala Santa 6 - 37129 Verona<br/>Codice fiscale: 93238110238 - i